OL,3,CYousaf warns against using new hate
OL,4,Ccrime law to make 'vexatious'
OL,5,Ccomplaints
OL,7,FScotland's First Minister has warned
OL,8,Fagainst using a controversial new hate
OL,9,Fcrime law to make "vexatious"
OL,10,Fcomplaints.
OL,12,FConcerns have been raised about the
OL,13,FHate Crime and Public Order (Scotland)
OL,14,FAct, which takes effect on Monday, and
OL,15,Fits potential impact on free speech.
