OL,3,CYousaf warns against using new hate
OL,4,Ccrime law to make 'vexatious'
OL,5,Ccomplaints
OL,7,FOpponents have suggested police could
OL,8,Fbe deluged with complaints against
OL,9,Fstatements people find offensive and
OL,10,Fsome, including senior SNP MP Joanna
OL,11,FCherry, have claimed that being under
OL,12,Fcriminal investigation could be a
OL,13,Fpunishment in itself.
OL,15,FThe First Minister has repeatedly said
OL,16,Fthat Police Scotland are able to deal
OL,17,Fwith vexatious complaints, but he told
OL,18,Fthe PA news agency the ramifications
OL,19,Fof making such a claim to police would
OL,20,Fbe "serious".
