OL,3,CYousaf warns against using new hate
OL,4,Ccrime law to make 'vexatious'
OL,5,Ccomplaints
OL,7,F"People have a right to report matters
OL,8,Fto the police if they believe a crime
OL,9,Fhas been committed," he said during a
OL,10,Fvisit to a soft play area in
OL,11,FCumbernauld, North Lanarkshire.
OL,13,F"And I would say to people the
OL,14,Flegislation makes it really clear what
OL,15,Fthe potential threshold for a crime
OL,16,Fwould be."
