OL,3,CYousaf warns against using new hate
OL,4,Ccrime law to make 'vexatious'
OL,5,Ccomplaints
OL,7,FThe legislation consolidates existing
OL,8,Fhate crime legislation and creates a
OL,9,Fnew offence of stirring up hatred in
OL,10,Frelation to protected characteristics,
OL,11,Falthough sex has been omitted in
OL,12,Ffavour of a standalone Bill designed
OL,13,Fto tackle misogyny.
OL,15,FIn order for an offence to be
OL,16,Fcommitted, the First Minister said, it
OL,17,Fwould have to be proven the accused
OL,18,Fhad intended to stir up hatred.
