OL,3,CYousaf warns against using new hate
OL,4,Ccrime law to make 'vexatious'
OL,5,Ccomplaints
OL,7,FSpeaking to journalists later, he
OL,8,Frejected suggestions it could go the
OL,9,Fway of other high-profile legislative
OL,10,FU-turns under the SNP, such as the
OL,11,Fnamed persons scheme and the Offensive
OL,12,FBehaviour at Football Act.
OL,14,F"It definitely won't (be repealed),"
OL,15,Fhe said.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@dO]
