OL,3,CYousaf warns against using new hate
OL,4,Ccrime law to make 'vexatious'
OL,5,Ccomplaints
OL,7,F"I'm very confident that we've got the
OL,8,Fbalance right between extending
OL,9,Fprotections to some of the most
OL,10,Fmarginalised groups who absolutely
OL,11,Fneed it, in a rising tide of hatred
OL,12,Fwe've seen right across the world and
OL,13,Fin many parts of Europe, including of
OL,14,Fcourse Scotland and the UK.
OL,16,F"But we've also got the balance right
OL,17,Fbetween that and making sure that
OL,18,Fwe've got freedom of expression
OL,19,Fprotections and safeguards within the
OL,20,Flegislation.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
