OL,3,CYousaf warns against using new hate
OL,4,Ccrime law to make 'vexatious'
OL,5,Ccomplaints
OL,7,F"I'm quite confident we've got a
OL,8,Freally robust piece of legislation and
OL,9,FI think there's been a lot of
OL,10,Fdisinformation and misinformation in
OL,11,Fthe last few weeks about it.
OL,13,F"And ultimately, once the Act comes
OL,14,Finto force, I think it will do exactly
OL,15,Fwhat we expect it to do, which is
OL,16,Fprotect the most marginalised in our
OL,17,Fcommunity."
